            "content": "Tile roofs (clay or concrete) are most popular in Tucson for good reason: excellent heat resistance, 50+ year lifespan, durability in monsoons, and aesthetic appeal. Flat roofs with white TPO membrane provide superior energy efficiency for ranch-style homes. Metal roofing Tucson AZ installations by standing seam metal roofers offer maximum durability and heat reflection with premium 22-24-26 gauge systems but higher upfront cost. We help you select roofing based on home style, budget, and long-term value."
